Package: Makurhini
Type: Package
Title: Makurhini: Analyzing landscape connectivity
Description: Makurhini (connect in Purépecha language) provides functions designed to estimate 
    landscape fragmentation and connectivity metrics and includes the ProtConn indicator that is
    used to report international connectivity targets.
Version: 3.0
